== Redmine plugin

This is a plugin for Redmine. Plugin adds tab 'Product' to the project, adds products's link to projects's issue. Product's tab has CRUD operation with product

== Installation

1. Copy the plugin directory into the "plugins" directory at the root
   of your Redmine directory

2. Migrate and copy plugin assets:
   bundle exec rake redmine:plugins:migrate

3. Start Redmine
4. Edit http://you.host.redmine/roles/permissions for plugin
